__section__
default
__description__
Create a link to a story, whenever it needs one

* dynamic = boolean for using dynamic, instead of static, page
* mode = comment mode
* threshold = comment threshold
* sid = story id
* section = story section
* text = text to put in link
__title__

__page__
misc
__lang__
en_US
__name__
linkStory
__template__
<A HREF="[% constants.rootdir %]/article.pl?sid=[% sid %]&mode=[% mode %]&threshold=[% threshold %]">[% text %]</A>
__seclev__
10000
